Package eu.monnetproject.mrd

Machine readable dictionary interfaces

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LexicalRelation
    A lexical relation, such as hypernym, antonym etc.
    LexicalRelationInstance
    An instance of a given lexical relationship between two elements
    MachineReadableDictionary
    Interface to a machine readable dictionary.
    MRDEntry
    A single entry in an MRD.
    Sense
    A sense that is attached to a generated lexical result.
    Synset
    A set of synonyms.
    TranslationRelation
    The lexical relation indicating a translation
